      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this impeccably preserved specimen, currently offered in showroom condition. This vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive maintenance, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure performance that is indistinguishable from new. For the collector or driver who demands nothing less than perfection, this motorcar offers an unparalleled acquisition opportunity.",
